genresAdvancedInfo.name: ukrainian classical
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre encompasses the rich history of classical music in Ukraine, with influences from both Western and Eastern musical traditions. It features orchestral works, chamber music, and solo pieces that showcase the technical and artistic abilities of Ukrainian composers and performers.
